## Adding New Parsers (TDD Workflow)

1. Add test fixtures in `__tests__/fixtures/notifications/{app-name}.json`
2. Write failing tests in `__tests__/infrastructure/notification/parsers/{app-name}.test.ts`
3. Create `src/infrastructure/notification/parsers/{app-name}.ts`
4. Implement the `NotificationParser` interface until tests pass
5. Refactor for clarity and edge cases
6. Register in `src/infrastructure/notification/parser-registry.ts`
